{"tid":1444790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我都認為要整休一星期，四大原因，追返文宣、加強凝聚力去避免麻木先","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:43.000Z","uid":110109,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"19955e5a372da6a9b38916abb4253ba93c8ad2e8","tid":1444790,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"有幾大原因<br />\n一、連續出動，身心一定有一定程度既疲倦。<br />\n<br />\n二、一路太多警黑事件發生，未煲大到一單下一單已經又出現，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣</span></strong>做嘢幾快都好，materials都未可以廣泛傳送出去。<br />\n<br />\n三、策略既檢討同方向既討論，大家都想可以喺一個信心、決心最強既時候出去抗爭，假如我地有一個更fine既策略（並非大台，但係會令群眾都安心，知道<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">進退將會有據，行動會更堅決有效，而唔係返到屋企，<span style=\"color: red;\">又有班軍師或者其他前線忿忿不平咁喺到話應該點點點</span></span></strong>&mdash;&mdash;先再討論一下，我覺得有益。<br />\n<br />\n四、民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實唔係話少左現有既民意，而其實係同第二點&mdash;&mdash;運動既速度減慢左我地吸納新民意既深度，我地未黎得切elaborate，甚至記者、資深傳媒人今日開個好po，都未比得曬所謂身邊淺黃睇，何況淺藍，我地要凝聚返身邊既戰友，文武兩路反擊。<br />\n<br />\n最後最後，我覺得我地確實只有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 1. 團結<br />\n2. 堅韌<br />\n<br />\n先係真正敵人冇既嘢<br />\n<br />\n每日既望天打卦，只會令我地抗爭情緒受影響。呢個抗爭係有排都唔會完既，各位共勉！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3fc3fbc20f18598bba889bbaff8f99fcf1ee1cc","tid":1444790,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd08512a6d217d88b4aa92afd10357d5d5de1d1f","tid":1444790,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:16:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44111d376c2871bec97d10bca53162f5a4ddce7f","tid":1444790,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:17:06.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"7b784c7b310ec574fb82e861ecdcfe3089fbffc8","tid":1444790,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823480b2cacf6c587810a6ff4145ea5ef2b2264f","tid":1444790,"uid":19871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd5ec508055b39c8391d230df25a81b112daaf44","tid":1444790,"uid":117968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bda4cd8e50146de29e7475424aa976b6c42714fc","tid":1444790,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"依家直頭需要諗新方式抗犬喇<br />\n放蛇<br />\n想我地忙於捉鬼 我地要諗方法！"}]}